# Android/iOS specific ignores live in `android/.gitignore` and
# `ios/App/.gitignore` (generated by `cap add android` / `cap add ios`).
# Here we cover only shell-level outputs that do not belong to a native
# project sub-tree.

# Capacitor CLI scratch directories
www/
dist/

# iOS build outputs (if `cap add ios` was run on a macOS checkout)
ios/App/build/
ios/App/Pods/
ios/App/App/public/
ios/DerivedData/
